{"tid":2231020,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請王茂俊（假韓寶生）交代一下點解代表其他英國手足又籌錢？","createTime":"2020-10-05T11:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T15:25:51.000Z","uid":57076,"like":50,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fd60cb7060d3af50b2486b10a5980a87109f3fdb","tid":2231020,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3zRH7p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3zRH7p.png&h=2f0a2256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WMq9uQt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWMq9uQt.png&h=21df10cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2U74iGk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2U74iGk.jpg&h=e921aa2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上見到圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BwN4iGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwN4iGm.jpg&h=afe05536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明王茂俊之前已經有係Patreon籌錢<br />\n<br />\n我認為燒國旗係手足應做既事，但王茂俊點解要無啦啦又「代表」英國手足籌錢？係咪要食兩家茶禮？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你籌咁多錢有無分比個十幾個被代表既手足？知唔知仲有好多個個係英國無人支援？<br />\n<br />\n我知有部分TG頻道係會幫住王茂俊，因為佢都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然我人丁單薄，但真係睇唔過眼佢想食英國手足人血饅頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔洗指控我五毛，可以起底睇到我以前出咩post<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">因為我就係其中一個英國手足，而且10.1 都有出，但王茂俊不代表我。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔會post 10.1相自爆，只可以post 英國影既生活想做證明。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QftLrX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9QftLrX.jpg&h=d1a6ed4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BeKiPx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BeKiPx.jpg&h=4634b5d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ca23c4c62e6662bb26166a466d85e7c5828a5f7","tid":2231020